title: Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J.Res. 101 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 04, 2010

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J.Res. 101





	On Saturday,December 4, 2010, the President signed into law:

	H.J.Res. 101, which provides FY 2011 appropriations through Saturday, December 18, 2010, for continuing projects and activities of the Federal Government provided under Public Law 111-242, the first FY 2011 Continuing Resolution.
